Also contains built in pause or play button.Key Specifications/Special Features:100% Brand New Fosmon Item.Built-in microphone for hands free conversations.High-Quality earphones for iPod, iPhone, iPad and all other MP3 players.Premium sound quality.Standard 3.5mm earphone plug fits all MP3 players with 3.5mm jack.Stylish design (non OEM) to fit your iPod, iPhone or other MP3players.Color: WhiteQty: 5Model Compatible:UniversalApple iPod Touch all generationApple iPhoneApple iPhone 3GApple iPhone 3GSApple iPhone 4S / 4Apple iPhone 5 5C 5S SEApple iPhone 6 6S 6 Plus 6S PlusApple iPad 1 / 2 / 3 / 4 / Air / ProApple iPad Mini 1 / 2 / 3Condition: Brand New
pTitle: 5 Pack of Earphone Mic for Apple iPhone 6 5S 5C 5 4S SE iPod iPad Earbud Headset
rText:
I'll be honest, if you're looking for sturdy earbuds that will stand the test of time (or last more than a month) these probably aren't for you. The rubber is weak and cracks after a few weeks if you don't take care of them. The earbuds themselves don't fit well in my ears. The sound quality isn't off the charts either but...  I still think they are worth the price I paid for it and will likely buy more.

If you're looking for a pack of disposable backups or if you're like me and you treat your earbuds pretty harshly all the time these prove to be more worthwhile. No matter how much I pay for earbuds I typically break them within a month. I'd rather spend the couple bucks per I'm spending on these than 20 to 50 I've paid before to still end up having to toss them after a month or so.

Overall you get what you pay for but I can tell that generally with a little care these can last as long or longer than many of the other cheaper earbuds out there.
rTitle: You get what you pay for

rText:
Overall I'm fine with the purchase. The cord is plenty long enough, which is better than Apple's short cord. The mic picks up my voice and little else. I don't know if it was intended to be a noise canceling mic, but it is behaving as one.

I will point out that the audio heard is a bit "tinny." If these will be used for MP3 players, keep that in mind.

These quality iLuv earphones feature a gold-plated 3.5mm stereo jack for superior conductivity and rust-resistance. Gold-plated 3.5mm stereo jack

pDescr:
Product Description 
Designed specifically for the Samsung Galaxy S6 & S6 Edge, these new Samsung earbuds provide you with clear sound whether listening to your favorite music, watching videos or making calls. They feature an ergonomic design built to easily slip into your ears and give you extra comfort while helping keep noise out. The flat cable prevents the earbuds from tangling so you can avoid those frustrating situations of having to de-tangle your earbuds. An inline control has an answer/end call button along with volume control and microphone so you can control your phone without having to take it our of your pocket. 

Features 
Ergonomic design for exceptional comfort thanks to hybrid earbuds 
Excellent sound quality thanks to wind and noise suppression 
Bass Boost class experience with dynamic 1-way driver 12mm 
Perfect for outdoor activities 
3-key operation volume / receiving calls 
Additional ear plugs sizes with comfortable fit 
Special cable design reduces cable clutter 
Type: Hybrid In-Ear Headset 
Drivers: 1-way dynamic 12mm 
Frequency range: 20Hz ~ 20kHz 
Impedance: 32 ohm 
Sensitivity: 98.5dB / mW at 1kHz 
Cable length: 1.2 m 

Charge or sync your Samsung phone or mobile device to your computer with this OEM original Samsung 1.5M Micro USB Cable. You can also use this cable with a USB power adapter (not included) or dock for fast charging. 

Features 
Authentic OEM Original Samsung Cable 
Non Retail Bulk Packaging 
1.5 meters/5 Feet in length 
Compatible with any device that accepts a micro-USB cable 
Sync and Charge capability

rText: Great product for the price! Bought for the headphones but USB charge cable was nice because it is extra long. After I got my fist pair I bought 2 more for my family. Received mine in a reasonable time frame.

pTitle: Samsung OEM Orginal Galaxy Inline Remote Earphones & USB Charge Sync 1.5M Cable
rText:
I purchased two of these as my wife's S6 headphone lost audio for headphone speaker. It works good and sound didn't seem any different from her original. This also works with my S4.

The USB cables actually came in very handy as my original S4 cable became defective and the S6 original thin USB cable was having issues charging either phones. S6 cable doesn't give enough electric charge and was displaying the error message of use original equipment BS. 

This product was cheap and a good replacement. Shipping was also quick.

MQbix Talking AeroFones Flat Cable Earphones will take listening to music to the next level. Designed to fit comfortably, this state-of-the-art accessory is noise isolating, so all you will hear is pure sound. The earphones with built in mic are an exceptional way to communicate with others. The integrated send/receive button will let you control the music and messages that you wish to send. With a tangle-free design, you won't have to worry about sorting out the cords. rText: I've been trying out many different headphones and earbuds lately. I am really pleased with this in-ear headphones. pDescr:
Take your workout to the next level with Powerbeats3 Wireless earphones, featuring up to 12 hours of battery life to last through multiple workouts and secure-fit earhooks to maximize comfort and stability. With Fast Fuel, a 5-minute charge gives you 1 hour of playback. Sweat and water resistance provides trusted durability and dual-driver acoustics deliver dynamic sound to power your workout. COMFORTABLY UNSTOPPABLE 
An improved ergonomic design makes way for clear, dynamic sound powered by dual-driver acoustics. Powerbeats3 Wireless comes with multiple eartips for a personalized and comfortable fit while flexible, secure-fit earhooks optimize stability. The result is authentic, wide-ranging sound with dynamic highs and powerful lows for an immersive listening experience. 
Requires iCloud account and macOS Sierra, iOS 10, or watchOS 3 
Key Features 
Connect via Class 1 Bluetooth with your device for wireless workout freedom
Up to 12 hours of battery life to power through multiple workouts
With Fast Fuel, a 5-minute charge gives you 1 hour of playback when battery is low
Sweat and water resistance to handle tough training
Flexible, secure-fit earhooks maximize comfort and stability
Dynamic, high-performance sound pushes you to the next level
Take calls, control your music and activate Siri with RemoteTalk 

What's in the Box? 
Powerbeats3 Wireless earphones
Eartips with four size options
Carrying case
Universal USB charging cable (USB-A to USB Micro-B)
Quick Start Guide
Warranty Card
pTitle: Powerbeats 3 Wireless Earphones
rText:
I had powerbeats 2 for 3 years, through dirt and grime and rough conditions they were impeccable! Finally they physically fell apart from too much chemical exposure and conditions were rough at my work. Had to buy the powerbeats 3 as walmart no longer carried the 2's. I was excited about the longer battery life and hoped for the best! This was a bad assumption.

Pros:
 Long battery life.

Cons: 
Super quiet compared to other beats headphones.

Arbitrarily stops playing sound and has to be turned off and paired back up.

No dust cover on charger port.

Again, ridiculously quiet even compared to cheaper headphones like skullcandy.

If you like beats for the ability to drown out everything and zone into your music, do NOT buy these, they have severely cut the decibel levels and thus are no longer worth any more than another pair of headphones at a cheaper price.
